text: Novoivanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kuganakbashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Sterlibashevo, 6 km from Kuganakbash. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Novoivanovka, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
